<strong>*L\u01b0u \u00fd:<\/strong><\/p>\n<p><em>&#8211; Kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng vui l\u00f2ng c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt app \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng ho\u1eb7c li\u00ean h\u1ec7 b\u01b0u c\u1ee5c \u0111ang ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3.<\/em><\/p>\n<p>T\u00edch h\u1ee3p 3 ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng t\u1ea1i app\/website ViettelPost, t\u00ednh n\u0103ng n\u00e0y gi\u00fap kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng <strong>QU\u1ea2N L\u00dd D\u00d2NG TI\u1ec0N<\/strong> hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3, d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng h\u01a1n, bao g\u1ed3m:<br \/>\n&#8211; <em><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong>Dashboard th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea ti\u1ec1n h\u00e0ng v\u00e0 c\u01b0\u1edbc ph\u00ed:<\/strong><\/span><\/em><br \/>\nV\u1edbi bi\u1ec3u \u0111\u1ed3 th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea minh b\u1ea1ch, tr\u1ef1c quan, th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng lu\u1ed3ng ti\u1ec1n v\u00e0 ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a doanh nghi\u1ec7p, ch\u1ee7 shop<br \/>\n&#8211; <span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><em><strong>Ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng R\u00fat ti\u1ec1n COD:<\/strong><\/em><\/span><br \/>\nGi\u00fap doanh nghi\u1ec7p ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng trong vi\u1ec7c r\u00fat ti\u1ec1n COD, c\u00f9ng h\u1ea1n m\u1ee9c r\u00fat l\u00ean t\u1edbi <strong>200 tri\u1ec7u\/ng\u00e0y<\/strong> v\u1edbi ph\u00ed h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ch\u1ec9 t\u1eeb 5.5K.<br \/>\n&#8211; <span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><em><strong>Ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng thanh to\u00e1n n\u1ee3 c\u01b0\u1edbc:<\/strong><\/em><\/span><br \/>\nThanh to\u00e1n n\u1ee3 c\u01b0\u1edbc nhanh ch\u00f3ng, v\u1edbi <strong>2 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ee9c thanh to\u00e1n<\/strong> ti\u1ec7n l\u1ee3i.<\/p>\n<h2><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: 14pt;\"><strong>1 . DASHBOARD TH\u1ed0NG K\u00ca TI\u1ec0N H\u00c0NG V\u00c0 C\u01af\u1edaC PH\u00cd:<\/strong><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>V\u1edbi c\u00e1c d\u00f2ng ti\u1ec1n v\u00e0 c\u01b0\u1edbc ph\u00ed \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng bi\u1ec3u \u0111\u1ed3 tr\u1ef1c quan, kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng s\u1ebd d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng n\u1eafm b\u1eaft th\u00f4ng tin v\u00e0 qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng kinh doanh hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 h\u01a1n.<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/viettelpost.com.vn\/tin-tuc\/linh-hoat-dong-tien-tai-chinh-chu-dong\/attachment\/cn-thong-ke\/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-17397\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-17397\" src=\"https:\/\/viettelpost.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/cn-thong-ke.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"282\" height=\"664\" \/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/viettelpost.com.vn\/tin-tuc\/linh-hoat-dong-tien-tai-chinh-chu-dong\/attachment\/cn-thong-ke-2\/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-17396\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-17396\" src=\"https:\/\/viettelpost.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/cn-thong-ke-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"310\" height=\"663\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: #ff0000;\"><strong>2 . CH\u1ee8C N\u0102NG R\u00daT TI\u1ec0N COD<\/strong><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>R\u00fat ti\u1ec1n COD l\u00e0 t\u00ednh n\u0103ng cho ph\u00e9p kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng<strong> ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng r\u00fat ti\u1ec1n COD<\/strong> v\u1ec1 t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n ng\u00e2n h\u00e0ng m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n, nhanh ch\u00f3ng. V\u1edbi t\u00ednh n\u0103ng R\u00fat ti\u1ec1n COD, kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng trong vi\u1ec7c ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t d\u00f2ng ti\u1ec1n, r\u00fat COD v\u00e0 thanh to\u00e1n c\u01b0\u1edbc ph\u00ed.<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/viettelpost.com.vn\/tin-tuc\/linh-hoat-dong-tien-tai-chinh-chu-dong\/attachment\/cn-rut-tien\/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-17393\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-17393\" src=\"https:\/\/viettelpost.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/cn-rut-tien.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"415\" height=\"897\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<h3><strong>Chi ti\u1ebft t\u00ednh n\u0103ng R\u00fat ti\u1ec1n COD<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p>&#8211; To\u